1
00:00:05,665 --> 00:00:08,885
A royal family, an ideally happy family.

2
00:00:08,926 --> 00:00:12,848
A high example of the unity of the home which is the foundation of national well-being.

3
00:00:13,868 --> 00:00:25,353
From that day in April 1923, when the wedding of the Duke of York and Lady Elizabeth Boeslein was solemnized at Westminster Abbey, this royal husband and wife have typified those stable things in life which are most worth having.

4
00:00:25,414 --> 00:00:32,356
A daughter was born, and the empire's rejoicing was a forecast of the affection that we now have for Princess Elizabeth and Princess Margaret Rose.

5
00:00:33,406 --> 00:00:39,090
Let us go back to those early days when the second son of King George V was a bachelor, a young man called Prince Albert.

6
00:00:39,869 --> 00:00:45,552
For him, life was a constant round of public duties, faithfully performed, with a word and a smile for everyone.

7
00:00:46,692 --> 00:00:53,155
As second son, Prince Albert might have passed his time pleasantly in the sports and luxuries of the well-to-do, but that was not his way.

8
00:00:53,915 --> 00:00:56,957
In those days, as in these, his aim was to do his duty.

9
00:01:00,874 --> 00:01:08,237
And later, a share of that duty was ably taken by the royal duchess, the gracious smiling lady who so quickly won her way into our hearts.

10
00:01:08,977 --> 00:01:14,081
In every part of the country, from Brighton to Inverness, they bore their part of the royal responsibility.

11
00:01:14,100 --> 00:01:16,602
Never did hospital or other charity call to them in vain.

12
00:01:17,263 --> 00:01:20,545
Here at Oxford with Lord Nuffield, her royal highness opened the infirmary.

13
00:01:23,341 --> 00:01:25,903
In industry, the Duke showed ever the keenest interest.

14
00:01:26,302 --> 00:01:29,763
He drove trains and trucks, and he started a giant turbo alternator.

15
00:01:30,543 --> 00:01:34,024
He was even offered the job of ironing a shirt, but he declared the risk was too great.

16
00:01:34,043 --> 00:01:36,965
His majesty has always been a keen tennis player.

17
00:01:36,984 --> 00:01:42,245
Here with Mr. Balfour, and at the same house party with Mr. Bonalore, he showed the form that later took him to Wimbledon.

18
00:01:48,444 --> 00:01:51,424
Vinterrelaksationen var en dag med hundarna och en fotbollsmatch.

19
00:01:51,444 --> 00:01:53,665
Och när sommaren kom igen var det en kokonutskärm.

20
00:01:53,686 --> 00:01:57,007
Duken tog del av de flesta formerna av sport.

21
00:01:57,328 --> 00:01:59,668
Och i nära allt visade han mer än den vanliga aptiteten.

22
00:01:59,688 --> 00:02:04,490
I New Romney och senare i Southwold såg vi början av vad som har blivit en nationell institution.

23
00:02:04,531 --> 00:02:07,412
Företagskampen som är deltagande av publica skolor och arbetsgivare.

24
00:02:15,774 --> 00:02:18,514
I 1920 visade prins Albert på bästdagen.

25
00:02:19,134 --> 00:02:20,634
Han tog sitt ställe i House of Lords.

26
00:02:21,215 --> 00:02:25,116
Resten av vår historia handlar om de tråkiga dagarna som skapade denna familj.

27
00:02:25,836 --> 00:02:28,937
Med kvinnan Mary och i andra dagar med hans fader, kring George.

28
00:02:29,217 --> 00:02:31,516
De här bilderna uppfattar många minnen.

29
00:02:31,697 --> 00:02:34,518
I Brussel presenterade duke DFC till kring Albert av Belgierna.

30
00:02:34,937 --> 00:02:36,677
Och sen stod det med prins Leopold.

31
00:02:36,698 --> 00:02:39,558
Två sonar, nu två kringar.

32
00:02:39,579 --> 00:02:43,199
Från Dunkirk har vi väljt en av de innanförbundna stjärnorna som byggdes av duke.

33
00:02:46,001 --> 00:02:47,681
på väg för det är Stefan.

34
00:02:47,801 --> 00:02:53,004
Australier fötterd, det röra brädan, bräggen med sunshine and smiles and cheers till London.

35
00:02:53,025 --> 00:02:55,306
Välkomna dem hemma igen med smiles and cheers.

36
00:02:55,325 --> 00:02:58,206
Det är not too much sunshine for crippled ex-servicemen.

37
00:02:58,288 --> 00:03:02,909
As with all those who are sick, the Duke and Duchess have a special consideration of many launches.

38
00:03:02,949 --> 00:03:07,512
We select this from 1928 when the Duchess of York launched the cruiser, which bears her name.

39
00:03:07,793 --> 00:03:09,432
And so the round of duty went on.

40
00:03:09,774 --> 00:03:09,954
St.

41
00:03:09,993 --> 00:03:10,593
James's Palace.

42
00:03:14,955 --> 00:03:16,015
öppning, Weymouth Bridge.

43
00:03:25,258 --> 00:03:26,018
Nottingham Pageant.

44
00:03:26,098 --> 00:03:28,397
By now Princess Elizabeth was growing up.

45
00:03:28,418 --> 00:03:31,359
She made a charming figure as bridesmaid at the wedding of Lady May Cambridge.

46
00:03:37,437 --> 00:03:42,960
At Glasgow, their royal highnesses received the honorary degree of Doctor of Laws and followed it with a little manual label.

47
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:48,281
One of the most memorable of our pictures was the ball at the Guild Hall, where the royal guests were received by Lord Derby.

48
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:51,822
At the jubilee of King George V, the Duke and Duchess attended with their daughters.

49
00:03:51,861 --> 00:03:54,362
Our King and Queen have travelled many times by plane.

50
00:03:54,983 --> 00:03:56,622
Here they are leaving for the fair at Brussels.

51
00:03:56,682 --> 00:04:00,663
It was also in Brussels that the Duke represented his father at the funeral of Queen Astrid.

52
00:04:00,683 --> 00:04:06,445
At the Armistice Day service in London, the Duke of York placed a wreath upon the cenotaph in memory of our million dead.

53
00:04:07,006 --> 00:04:10,268
Hommage from one who shared equally the hazards of war at the battle of Jutland.

54
00:04:15,189 --> 00:04:17,170
And a last sad tribute to a great king.

55
00:04:17,571 --> 00:04:24,754
With his brothers he marched in the funeral cortege of George V. How soon after that were the affairs of our royal family to change again.

56
00:04:25,514 --> 00:04:29,857
By an instrument of abdication to the government led by Mr Baldwin, Edward renounced the monarchy.

57
00:04:30,237 --> 00:04:32,418
Albert, duke of York, became king George VI.

58
00:04:33,158 --> 00:04:35,339
All our thoughts were with him on that night of his accession.

59
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:37,920
En kungafamilj och en lycklig familj.

60
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:41,283
Ett gott exempel på en nations fastaste grundval.

61
00:04:41,324 --> 00:04:42,444
Ett gott hem.

62
00:05:06,249 --> 00:05:16,812
Allt sedan den dag i april 1923 när bröllopet mellan härtigen av York och Lady Elizabeth Bowes Lyon firades i Westminster Abbey har dessa kungliga makar varit ett föredöme i allt.

63
00:05:22,934 --> 00:05:31,276
Redan vid den första dotterns födelse visade hela imperiet den tillgivenhet som sedan dess alltid kommit småprinsessorna Elisabeth och Margaret Rose till del.

64
00:05:32,084 --> 00:05:37,913
Låt oss gå tillbaka till den tid då konung Georg Vs andra son ännu var unka, ungeprins Albert.

65
00:05:38,713 --> 00:05:42,478
Som andra sonen i familjen kunde han länga sitt liv uteslutande åt sport och nöjen.

66
00:05:43,098 --> 00:05:44,420
Men det passade inte hans karaktär.

67
00:05:45,663 --> 00:05:48,846
Då och liksom nu var hans enda strävan att göra sin plikt.

68
00:06:46,221 --> 00:06:48,920
Sjukvård och välgörenhet behövde aldrig saknas på skydd.

69
00:06:49,822 --> 00:06:51,802
Här ser vi att det innan öppnade ett sjukhus i Oxford.

70
00:06:55,882 --> 00:06:59,125
Härtingen visade alltid stort intresse vid besöken i landets industrier.

71
00:07:47,456 --> 00:07:49,117
Han har alltid varit ivrig tennisspelare.

72
00:07:50,177 --> 00:07:54,577
Här syns han med gamle premiärministern Lord Balfour och Bonar Law vid privattennis.

73
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:59,060
Men även på Wimbledon har han spelat.

74
00:08:00,261 --> 00:08:02,122
På vintern fann han avspänning i jakter.

75
00:08:17,673 --> 00:08:21,956
Färdigheten deltog i nästan all sport och visade överallt mer än vanlig fallenhet.

76
00:08:35,086 --> 00:08:39,807
Injo Romney såg i början till vad som senare blivit den hela landets angelägenhet.

77
00:08:40,647 --> 00:08:44,427
Ferielägren för pojkar från fabriker och landets förnämsta skolor.

78
00:08:45,288 --> 00:08:48,389
Där härtingens personliga insats säkrade företagets framgång.

79
00:08:56,577 --> 00:08:56,717
I. I. I. I.

80
00:09:28,361 --> 00:09:56,804
1920 tog prins Albert sitt i parlamentet Här med drottning Mary Och med sin fader vid tillfällen som nationen alltid ska minnas I Bryssel på officiellt besök hos kong Albert

81
00:09:58,527 --> 00:10:02,590
Här tillsammans med prins Leopold, två prinsar, nu två konungar.

82
00:10:05,812 --> 00:10:08,673
I Australien mottogs han och han smakar med solsken och jubel.

83
00:10:23,543 --> 00:10:27,826
Liksom det vid sin återkomst till England möttes av välkomnande jubel, fast inte så mycket solsken.

84
00:10:35,952 --> 00:10:40,214
För krigsinvalider, liksom för alla sjuka, har härtigparat visat särskilt deltagande.

85
00:10:57,998 --> 00:11:01,359
Redan tidigt började prinsessan Elisabeth delta i det offentliga livet.

86
00:11:09,265 --> 00:11:12,369
I Glasgow kreerades härtigparet till Giverys hedersdoktorer.

87
00:11:21,277 --> 00:11:24,220
Vid den stora ballen i Guildhall minnas vi dem i sällskap med Lord Davy.

88
00:11:39,076 --> 00:11:42,976
Och här gör den femtes jubileum som Hattiparet firade med hela sin familj.

89
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:02,900
Deras majestäter använder sig gärna av flyget.

90
00:12:03,522 --> 00:12:04,922
Här på väg till mässan i Bryssel.

91
00:12:14,923 --> 00:12:18,025
Där representerade också härtigen sin fader vid drottning Astrids begravning.

92
00:12:25,751 --> 00:12:33,937
På vapenstilleståndsdagen nedlade härtigen en krans vid scenotafiet i London till minne av den miljon av landets söner som stupat i världskriget.

93
00:12:35,241 --> 00:12:37,628
Själv deltog han som en av de många i göttlandradningen.

94
00:12:40,335 --> 00:12:43,822
Och till slut en sista hedersbetygelse till sin fader och konung.

95
00:12:44,591 --> 00:12:47,471
Med sina bröder till fots i Georg Vs begravningståg.

96
00:12:48,052 --> 00:12:50,734
Men snart skulle kungafamiljens öden växla än en gång.

97
00:12:51,453 --> 00:13:02,278
Genom sin abdikation som inlämnas till regeringschefen Baldwin avsades konung Edvard kronan och prins Albert, hertigen av York, blev Georg VI.

98
00:13:02,458 --> 00:13:05,740
1936 var ett oblyckligt och osäkert år för det brittiska imperiet.

99
00:13:06,321 --> 00:13:14,833
Men 1937 krönes en konung som äger alla de förutsättningar en god husfader har för att bli en god landsfader.
